== pawfaliki-0.1.0 (10/08/2004) ==
* Initial version of everything.

== pawfaliki-0.2.0 (10/11/2004) ==
* Added CSS support.
* Fixed wordwrapping bugs.
* Fixed coloured text bugs.
* Everything should be transitional html4.0 compliant.
* Added licensing information.
* Added locking page support.

== pawfaliki-0.3.0 (11/11/2004) ==
* Rewritten parser maintains whitespace without having to use the <PRE> tag.
* All pages are now html4.01 strict compliant.
* Ip blocking now enabled. Even works with wildcards.

== pawfaliki-0.4.0 (**/**/****) ==
* Multiple license support.
* Better error handling on writing pages.
* Wiki syntax info block on edit page.
* Specify wiki pages using [[]] tags.
* Ability to disable auto-generated WikiLinks (disabled by default).
* Restricted access support with password protection.
* Support for targets in web links.
* Use images in links.
* New wiki syntax for page anchors.
* Support for HTML in wiki pages (disabled by default).
